In a message dated 8/22/2004 5:03:10 AM Eastern Daylight Time,
AlwaysLearning@yahoogroups.com writes:
I could put down a "splat mat" in the living room but I don't have one.
I'd have to buy one, and I don't get out much. Plus I'm broke. Maybe my
MIL will get me one if I ask.
*************Go to your local big box hardware store and int he paint
department they have plastic disposable drop cloths. I think They are about 3 bucks.
I bet you could find three bucks in change around the house!

Elissa Jill
